-- ING shares down more than 15 percent
-- 
-- Fri Oct 17, 2008 5:13am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/17/us-ing-shares-idUSTRE49G24Q20081017

 

 AMSTERDAM  (Reuters) - Shares in Dutch financial services group ING Groep NV ( ING.AS )( ING.N ) dived more than 15 percent on Friday and the company said it had no comment on the share price move. 

 ING shares traded at 8.50 euros at 5:05 a.m. EDT, down 15.6 percent, after touching 8.15 euros earlier in the session. (Reporting by  Gilbert Kreijger )